{"title":"Specialized Celebrates 50 Years w/ Beautiful Limited S-Works Forward 50 Collection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/specialized-celebrates-50-years-imited-s-works-forward-50-collection/","date":1721939767000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Hero.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" alt=\"(Photos / Specialized Bicycles)\" /></p>\n<p>Northern California’s own <a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/us/en\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized Bicycles</a> has been doing what they do for 50 years. That’s pretty impressive. Today they announced they are celebrating this milestone by releasing their all-new <a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/us/en/shop/forward-50-ltd\" target=\"_blank\">limited S-Works Forward 50 Collection</a>, in hopes of inspiring the next 50 years of innovation. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-heat-and-time.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-heat-and-time.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection tarmac heat and time\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-heat-and-time.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-heat-and-time-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-heat-and-time-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-heat-and-time-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-heat-and-time-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Specialized Bicycles)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The collection combines performance with stunning good looks. Gold represents Specialized Bicycles’ 50th year and “how their desire to improve lives through riding has not lost an ounce of luster”.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-heat-and-time.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-heat-and-time.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection heat and time\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-heat-and-time.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-heat-and-time-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-heat-and-time-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-heat-and-time-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-heat-and-time-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The pink is a throwback to the historic, OG Team Stumpjumper and their “commitment to racing with irreverent and rebellious spirit”. This collection represents the “ultimate expression of the innovate or die attitude” that has inspired Specialized for the last 50 years.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>When you look at the essence of Specialized, it’s clear we are born from a rebellious spirit and attitude that continues to challenge the industry. That spirit is something that lit a fire inside Mike 50 years ago, and it is that same desire and confidence we carry now to carve out the next 50 years.</em>” – Kayla Clarot, Leader of Brand Concepts</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The S-Works Forward 50 Collection encapsulates Specialized’s 50 years in four products that represent the pinnacle of today’s performance products. “Every ounce of knowledge and technology was poured in to create the highest-performing bikes and equipment for our riders, period. They contain our history and predict our future.”</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Specialized Bicycles view the Tarmac SL, Epic World Cup, Evade 3, and Prevail 3 not as endpoints but as beginnings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Forward 50 LTD Collection Bicycles</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-floating.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-floating.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection tarmac floating\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-floating.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-floating-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-floating-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-floating-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-floating-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>S-Works Tarmac SL8 Forward 50 LTD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-floating-epic.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-floating-epic.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection floating epic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-floating-epic.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-floating-epic-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-floating-epic-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-floating-epic-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-floating-epic-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>S-Works Epic World Cup Forward 50 LTD</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>The S-Works Tarmac SL8 Forward 50 LTD</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $16,500</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-front-side.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-front-side.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection tarmac front side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-front-side.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-front-side-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-front-side-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-front-side-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-front-side-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>S-Works Tarmac SL8 Forward 50 LTD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>Tamac SL8 was designed with the knowledge that aerodynamics or lightweight alone don’t win races—speed is what matters. It represents Specialized’s ability to look beyond the entrenched categories of aero, weight, and gender to focus on delivering what the rider needs to win”. </em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-fork.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-fork.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection tarmac fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-fork.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-fork-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-fork-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-fork-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-fork-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-back-side.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-back-side.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection tarmac back side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-back-side.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-back-side-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-back-side-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-back-side-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-tarmac-back-side-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Only 250 bikes will be available worldwide. These S-Works Tarmac SL8 Forward 50 LTD bikes are delivered with the following: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Rapide CLX II Team wheels</li>\n\n\n\n<li>S-Works Power with Mirror saddle</li>\n\n\n\n<li>S-Works Tarmac SL8 seatpost</li>\n\n\n\n<li>All custom painted to match the frame</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Turbo clinchers</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Rapide cockpit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shimano Dura-Ace 12-speed group</li>\n\n\n\n<li>CeramicSpeed bearings</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>S-Works Epic World Cup Forward 50 LTD</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $14,000</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-epic-front-side.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-epic-front-side.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection epic front side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-epic-front-side.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-epic-front-side-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-epic-front-side-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-epic-front-side-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-epic-front-side-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>S-Works Epic World Cup Forward 50 LTD</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>Epic World Cup is a purpose-built machine, and its purpose is to win. We challenged ourselves to eschew the conventional understanding of what it takes to be the fastest and rose to that challenge with an unprecedented integrated system approach to chassis engineering, revolutionary shock design, and peerless ride dynamics</em>.”</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Sid.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Sid.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection Sid\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Sid.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Sid-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Sid-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Sid-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Sid-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Epic-world-cup-back-side.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Epic-world-cup-back-side.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection Epic world cup back side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Epic-world-cup-back-side.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Epic-world-cup-back-side-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Epic-world-cup-back-side-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Epic-world-cup-back-side-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-Epic-world-cup-back-side-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Only 250 bikes will be available worldwide. These S-Works World Cup Epic Forward 50 LTD bikes are delivered with the following: </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>RockShox SIDLuxe WCID rear shock</li>\n\n\n\n<li>RockShox SID SL Ultimate 3P fork</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Roval Control SL Team wheelset</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Roval Control SL integrated cockpit</li>\n\n\n\n<li> Roval Control SL seatpost</li>\n\n\n\n<li>S-Works Power with Mirror saddle</li>\n\n\n\n<li>CeramicSpeed DUB bottom bracket</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Forward 50 LTD Collection Helmets</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-helmets.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-helmets.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection helmets\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-helmets.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-helmets-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-helmets-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-helmets-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-helmets-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>S-Works Prevail 3 Forward 50 LMD Helmet</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $350</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-top-side.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-top-side.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection prevail top side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-top-side.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-top-side-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-top-side-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-top-side-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-top-side-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>S-Works Prevail 3 Forward 50 LMD Helmet</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>“<em>S-Works Prevail 3 is the perfect helmet for riders who value the comfort and performance delivered by superior ventilation. It is the ultimate all-around helmet that excels in hot conditions, strenuous climbs, and mountainous stages. We built a helmet that would keep you safe and never let you down – rain or shine, heat or snow. With limited supply worldwide, S-Works Prevail 3 Forward 50 LTD represents our unwavering commitment to the next 50 years of innovation</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail.jpeg\" alt=\"Specialized Bicycles Foward 50 Collection prevail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Specialized-Bicycles-Foward-50-Collection-prevail-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bi